{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that evening, evidently, I, I didn't-- I, I just didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- and I can't forgive myself why I didn't have a piece of bread on me when I went to see him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that-- after that tearful, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] tearful goodbye episode, I, I went out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and I remember saying something to, to-- the guard said, did you find your dad?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I found him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I says, hey, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stood at attention and thanked him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I was at least thankful to him that he let me see my dad, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As painful as it was, at least I got to say goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even though he kept saying it, I don't know whether he believed in it himself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he was just-- he was just telling me that things would be OK.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's going to a different place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'll take care of his sores and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, they took care of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who knows if he was alive 24 hours later?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That camp-- Dyhernfurth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, in the winter of '43, '44, I was evacuated for another camp, also by the same name and just in the outskirts of town where we used to-- where I used to mix mortar and carry cement blocks.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had no idea what we were building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was some kind of a building we were building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As it turned out, we were building the barracks, where we moved in ourselves into that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came-- this, this camp was, was Dyhernfurth II.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
